{"tid":1944353,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[易碎]生化危機 3 重製版保險箱密碼為「918」中國玩家感覺冒犯揚言抵制","createTime":"2020-03-26T10:22:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T10:28:03.000Z","uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"58721ed0967afa2608962362aa29d8c628b7ed87","tid":1944353,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T10:22:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/03/26/biohazard-re3-918/game-channel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F03%2F26%2Fbiohazard-re3-918%2Fgame-channel%2F&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWR%2Fkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=8a39cfdf\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/03/26/biohazard-re3-918/game-channel/</a><br />\n<br />\n近日 Capcom 推出了《生化危機 3 重製版》的試玩版，以讓大家體驗重製版與舊作的分別。不過，有中國玩家遊玩過後指，遊戲內的密碼數字有冒犯中國之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/ae5924c0-6db4-11ea-a6fd-84401f5f4161-scaled.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2Fae5924c0-6db4-11ea-a6fd-84401f5f4161-scaled.jpeg&h=657a4da9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n《生化危機 3 重製版》試玩版的遊玩時間只有 5 分鐘左右，當中有個關卡需要在保險箱上輸入密碼，而密碼提示印在一張海報上，玩家推測後可得出三位密碼「918」。<br />\n<br />\n有中國玩家就指此數字讓其聯想到被日軍侵占的九一八事變，直感冒犯。更有中國玩家表示，如正式版未有對此作出修正，便會作出給《還願》和《我的英雄學院》一樣的差評。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/螢幕截圖-2020-03-26-下午4.10.50-1280x576.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2020-03-26-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%884.10.50-1280x576.png&h=b21ae038&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過，不少中國玩家與台灣玩家都認為這件事情過於牽強，並質疑是否與中國歷史有關的數字，如「64」、「128」等都通通不能使用，指某部份中國玩家過於「玻璃心」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/螢幕截圖-2020-03-26-下午4.15.42-869x900.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2020-03-26-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%884.15.42-869x900.png&h=cd1d196c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1142e8d8b84a20ae48c5b05d7aad6f95d537e136","tid":1944353,"uid":321837,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T10:28:03.000Z","msg":"中國人好下作卑劣.<br />\n咩都有得嘈. 求其一串數字裡面有八,九, 六,四, 一...........佢都可以借頭借路嘈並且恐嚇對方."}]}